y in the north of Italy. Mountains and lakes are just around the corner. For further information and informal inquiries please do not hesitate to contact me (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"mailto:d.gerosa@bham.ac.uk\" target=\"_blank\">d.gerosa@bham.ac.uk<\/a>).&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The University of Milano-Bicocca&nbsp;welcomes applications for Ph.D. scholarships. The application deadline is June 16th, 2021 for positions to start later in 2021: https:\/\/en.unimib.it\/education\/doctoral-research-phd-programmes\/how-apply-phd-programme In particular, I am looking for a strong, highly motivated candidate to join my newly established research &hellip; <a href=\"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/2021\/05\/18\/come-to-milan-for-a-phd\/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&rarr;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":true,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_coblocks_attr":"","_coblocks_dimensions":"","_coblocks_responsive_height":"","_coblocks_accordion_ie_support":"","spay_email":""},"categories":[10,11],"tags":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","amp_validity":null,"amp_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4287"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4287"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4287\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4299,"href":"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4287\/revisions\/4299"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4287"